            "text_9wCkMA": {
              "type": "text",
              "settings": {
                "text": "<p></p><p><strong>Sip-Sip Hooray® </strong>is a women-owned & operated drinkware company based in southern Louisiana, <strong>creating feel-good, quality-driven products </strong>since 2023. Our designs are created in-house, produced in small batches, and packed with care.</p><p></p><p>We believe <strong>everyday moments deserve to be celebrated</strong>; and something as simple as your favorite cup can turn the ordinary into something special. Each piece is designed with care and backed by purpose.</p><p>Through our <em><strong>Pour-it Forward</strong></em><strong>™ </strong>program, we donate a portion of every order to a new cause each month. So, when you shop with us, <strong>you're not just treating yourself, you're helping someone else, too.</strong></p><p>We’re deeply grateful for every order and pour our hearts into everything we make. If anything isn’t just right, we’re here to make it right, <strong>because you matter to us.</strong></p>",
